MIFARE SmartHack Utils - Tools to aid in attacking smarter MIFARE tags


See COPYING for license information.  Based on sources included in libnfc by
Romuald Conty and libfreefare by Romain Tartiere.

nfc-mfdesfire - Enumerate AIDs and other info  on a DESFire tag
nfc-mfdesfire-keysearch - Search for keys using an input data file against
	a specified AID and key index number.
nfc-mfultralightc
	Read or write data to an Ultralight-C/Ultralight-X tag.

INSTALL

These tools require the libnfc and libfreefare libraries.  Run "make" to build.

